rows.label: qst202804_0010
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Ugh...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0020
rows.name: This place is crawling with Parisax...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0030
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]Parisax?

rows.label: qst202804_0040
rows.name: This is a tough place for Menou...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0050
rows.name: What should we do? Should we turn back?

rows.label: qst202804_0060
rows.name: I'll be fine.

rows.label: qst202804_0070
rows.name:
This many shouldn't be
a problem at all...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0080
rows.name:
The ore I'm searching for
must be deep inside...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0090
rows.name:
I have no intention of turning
back after coming this far.

rows.label: qst202804_0100
rows.name: Now, let's go.

rows.label: qst202804_0110
rows.name:
I'll be fine as long as
I don't get close...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0120
rows.name:
Let's move slowly so we
don't provoke them...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0130
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Eek!

rows.label: qst202804_0140
rows.name: [ML:undisp ][ML:Dash ]!!!!

rows.label: qst202804_0150
rows.name: Menou, are you all right?

rows.label: qst202804_0160
rows.name: No good...[ML:Dash ] She's passed out.

rows.label: qst202804_0170
rows.name: We cannot afford to be held up here.

rows.label: qst202804_0180
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]Let's fall back for now.

rows.label: qst202804_0190
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]Huh? Did I...[ML:Dash ] faint?

rows.label: qst202804_0200
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]I'm sorry.

rows.label: qst202804_0210
rows.name: Don't worry about it so much.

rows.label: qst202804_0220
rows.name:
Yeah, everyone has something
they're not good at.

rows.label: qst202804_0230
rows.name: But...[ML:Dash ] it's pathetic...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0240
rows.name:
I'm making you all put up with my selfish
wishes, and then I go and faint...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0250
rows.name: But what should we do now, mo?

rows.label: qst202804_0260
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Hmm...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0270
rows.name: [ML:undisp ][ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0280
rows.name:
How about we wipe out the Parisax,
and then Menou comes in after?

rows.label: qst202804_0290
rows.name:
No, that won't do...[ML:Dash ] I have to
clear the way with my own hands...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0300
rows.name: But you're terrified of bugs, mo?

rows.label: qst202804_0310
rows.name: That's true, but...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0320
rows.name:
Then how about you fight with
your eyes closed, Menou?

rows.label: qst202804_0330
rows.name:
I might accidentally
attack one of you...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0340
rows.name:
Usually, Menou, you help
many of our allies.

rows.label: qst202804_0350
rows.name:
In times like these, it would not be
wrong to rely on your allies, would it?

rows.label: qst202804_0360
rows.name: That's true, but...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0370
rows.name: What a difficult personality.

rows.label: qst202804_0380
rows.name:
But that just shows how
strong her will is.

rows.label: qst202804_0390
rows.name:
That's right. I guess there's nothing
for it but for Menou to do it.

rows.label: qst202804_0400
rows.name: I suppose so...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0410
rows.name:
Talking with all of you
has made me realize...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0420
rows.name:
I really want to go forward with my
own hands and find a new ore...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0430
rows.name:
I got scared when the bugs I hate
appeared, but that's not right.

rows.label: qst202804_0440
rows.name:
No matter how difficult the challenge, I have
to summon my courage and break through.

rows.label: qst202804_0450
rows.name: Things are heating up.

rows.label: qst202804_0460
rows.name: Yes, Menou has regained her composure.

rows.label: qst202804_0470
rows.name: Yes...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202804_0480
rows.name: Everyone, can we try one more time?

rows.label: qst202804_0490
rows.name: Of course.

rows.label: qst202804_0500
rows.name:
I'll do my best to support
you, so let's go all out.

rows.label: qst202804_0510
rows.name:
Thank you...[ML:Dash ] This time, I
will see my will through.
